title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 4/13 - Florio/Finch
description: The show opens with Florio's weekly spot, but the rest of the hour is devoted to the Howlllll, as the Wolves won their play-in game last night to snag the 7th seed in the playoffs. Wolves coach Chris Finch wraps the opening hour!
